Privacy Policy
Last updated: September 5, 2024
1. Introduction
Welcome to Feynman AI ("we," "our," or "us"). We are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application Feynman AI (the "App").
2. Information We Collect
We collect the following types of information:
2.1 Personal Information
• Email address
• Profile picture
2.2 Usage Data
We collect usage data related to your interactions with the App, including:
• Speaking content data
• Conversation scenarios used
• AI-generated responses
• User preferences and settings
• App usage statistics (e.g., frequency of use, features accessed)
2.3 Device and Advertising Data
We use AppsFlyer, a third-party analytics service, to collect certain data for advertising and analytics purposes. This data may include:
• Device identifiers
• Advertising identifiers
3. How We Use Your Information
We use your information for the following purposes:
• To provide and maintain our App
• To personalize your experience and improve our services
• To notify you about changes to our App
• To allow you to participate in interactive features of our App when you choose to do so
• To provide customer support
• To gather analysis or valuable information so that we can improve our App
• To monitor the usage of our App
• To detect, prevent and address technical issues
4. Data Storage and Security
Your data is stored on Amazon Web Services (AWS) servers located in the United States. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to maintain the security of your personal information.
5. Data Retention and Deletion
We will retain your personal information only for as long as is necessary for the purposes set out in this Privacy Policy. When you delete your account, all your personal information and usage data will be permanently deleted from our servers.
6. Your Data Protection Rights
You have the right to:
• Access your personal data
• Correct your personal data
• Delete your account and associated data
To exercise these rights, please go to the Profile section in the App or contact us at support@feynmanai.net.
7. Children's Privacy
Our App is intended for users who are 13 years of age or older. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are between 13 and 18 years old, you may use our App only with parental or guardian consent and supervision.
8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and sending you a notification within the App.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
Email: support@feynmanai.net
Website: feynmanai.net
We use cookies that are essential for our site to work. To improve our site, we would like to use additional cookies to help us understand how visitors use it, measure traffic to our site from social media platforms and to personalise your experience. Some of the cookies that we use are provided by third parties. To accept all cookies click "Accept". To reject all optional cookies click "Reject".
